  <body>
    <p>This is the internal technical documentation for the Sámi pedagogical project. It is written by the project members, mainly for the project members, in order to keep track of things. Teacher and user documentation is found at <a href="http://giellatekno.uit.no/oahpa">giellatekno.uit.no/oahpa/</a>. For the time being it is in Sámi only (but most games are documented in English at the <a href="http://visl.sdu.dk/">visl.sdu.dk</a> site), but documentation in other languages are forthcoming.</p>

